CONTEXT:
After two whole years and over two million views, UMG decided it’d be fun to remove the documentary I spent four months of my life crafting. With the sheer amount of claims, I don’t know which one specifically got it taken down, which is why I opted not to appeal and instead took this as an opportunity to make the video better and longer than it was before. I’ve added more analysis, full coverage of Donda, and of course done my best to remove every bit of claimable music I stupidly included the first time. I know this isn’t a completely new video, but I’ve gotten numerous requests to bring this one back since the day it was deleted. It’s always been a personal favorite of mine and I wanted to do what I could to restore it. I know some ppl won’t care but for the ones that do, I hope you enjoy. Thanks for reading this mess of a tangent.
